  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Combine the best of city, lake and mountains on this multi-centre holiday starting in Salzburg</h2>
<p>A multi-centre holiday <a data-udi="umb://document/2631ac5f3f824554a6f8c73491b2efae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2631ac5f3f824554a6f8c73491b2efae}" title="Zell am See"></a> means you get to experience some Austria's best bits with varied scenery and plenty to explore along the way. Spend a couple of days exploring the cultural hub of <a data-udi="umb://document/31b86014d3b04c3da584cc56dca63c66" href="/{localLink:umb://document/31b86014d3b04c3da584cc56dca63c66}" title="Salzburg">Salzburg</a>, packed with history, art and music. Then, pick from a choice of Austrian destinations for the second half of your holiday - perhaps a few days exploring the delights of <a data-udi="umb://document/2631ac5f3f824554a6f8c73491b2efae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2631ac5f3f824554a6f8c73491b2efae}" title="Zell am See">Zell am See</a> with it's picturesque location on the shores of Lake Zell. Enjoy the views of the Salzkammergut, known as "Austria's Lake District" in <a data-udi="umb://document/d2df326fd2d544f2b9d4699c3cf10233" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d2df326fd2d544f2b9d4699c3cf10233}" title="Fuschl am See">Fuschl</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/95ff1fe2e71242759843cc1f6b11ccdc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/95ff1fe2e71242759843cc1f6b11ccdc}" title="St. Gilgen">St. Gilgen</a>, or, head to <a data-udi="umb://document/085c5cbb87794e7c9ca8a69475a257df" href="/{localLink:umb://document/085c5cbb87794e7c9ca8a69475a257df}" title="Soll">Söll</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/770717fcbb524fc8b57e0feef58fcce0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/770717fcbb524fc8b57e0feef58fcce0}" title="Ellmau">Ellmau</a> and hike amongst the rolling hills and dramatic peaks of the Wilder Kaiser mountains.</p>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options: </h3>
<ul>
<li style="list-style-type: none;">
<ul>
<li>Travel and change destination on a Wednesday or Saturday</li>
<li>Combine stays of 3, 4, 7, 10 or 11 nights into a total holiday duration of 7, 10, 11 or 14 nights</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK</li>
<li>Transfers from the airport to your hotel in Salzburg, from your hotel in Salzburg to your hotel in your second destination and from your hotel in your second destination to the airport</li>
<li>Accommodation in your chosen hotel in each destination</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<p> </p>
