  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Hotels in Salzburg</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/805fe48c88cd43b39dbd7a4500f74e3c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/805fe48c88cd43b39dbd7a4500f74e3c}" title="Arte Hotel Salzburg">Arte Hotel</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 300px; height: 200px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13108475/arte-hotel-salzburg-bar.jpg?width=300&amp;height=200" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/464f05c437c243128829a2a1b2c51791" />The stylish Arte Hotel is located close to Salzburg train station and within easy walking distance of the famous Mirabell Gardens. Rooms have everything you need for a comfortable stay and are complimented by exceptional views across the city from the bar and restaurant. This is all topped off by a small spa with sauna, relaxation area and fitness room.</p>
