  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Add on a few days in Salzburg to the start of your Inghams walking holiday. As the birthplace of Mozart, Salzburg is a hub of music and culture, with a multitude of museums and galleries to discover, plus the impressive Fortress which stands proudly above the city skyline.</p>]]></listingDescription>
