  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p>A multi-centre holiday lets you mix and match hotels, lengths of stay, and exciting activities to create your ideal trip. Enjoy everything from panoramic walks, cultural tours and outdoor adventures to relaxing days and tasty local cuisine.</p>
<h3>Visit the cultural city of Salzburg and explore the city sights</h3>
<p>Salzburg is famously the filming destination for many scenes in the film "Sound of Music" including the Mirabell Gardens. Wander the cobbled streets of the historic Old Town, spot Mozart's birthplace, enjoy a river cruise and discover some of the beautiful walking trails that weave through the city and its outskirts - there's lots to discover in this beautiful and bustling part of Austria.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/31b86014d3b04c3da584cc56dca63c66" href="/{localLink:umb://document/31b86014d3b04c3da584cc56dca63c66}" title="Salzburg" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">Find Out More About Salzburg</a></p>
<h2>Choose your second destination:</h2>
<p>For your second destination, you can pick from a choice of fantastic Austrian destinations:</p>
<ul>
<li>Kitzbühel</li>
<li>St. Johann</li>
<li>Söll</li>
<li>Oberau</li>
<li>Westendorf</li>
<li>Ellmau</li>
<li>Saalbach Hinterglemm</li>
<li>Zell am See</li>
<li>Fuschl am See</li>
<li>Gilgen</li>
<li>Filzmoos</li>
</ul>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<h3>Flights and transfers</h3>
<p>Your first destination is Salzburg, and your outbound flight will be into Salzburg airport - on arrival you'll get a taxi transfer from Salzburg airport to your hotel (approx. 25-30 minutes). </p>
<p>The transfer from Salzburg to your second destination will vary depending on the destination:</p>
<ul>
<li>Salzburg to Kitzbühel</li>
<li>Salzburg to St. Johann</li>
<li>Salzburg to Söll</li>
<li>Salzburg to Oberau</li>
<li>Salzburg to Westendorf</li>
<li>Salzburg to Ellmau</li>
<li>Salzburg to Saalbach Hinterglemm</li>
<li>Salzburg to Zell am See</li>
<li>Salzburg to Fuschl am See</li>
<li>Salzburg to St. Gilgen</li>
<li>Salzburg to Filzmoos</li>
</ul>
<p>Your flight home will be from Salzburg airport, and the transfer to the airport will be a shared Inghams coach transfer.</p>
<p><em>Please note: This is an independent multi-centre holiday and you are free to choose your own itinerary in each destination. The above contains recommendations which are provided for information only and are not included in the price of your holiday. An Inghams Destination Expert will be on hand locally either in resort or by telephone and will provide advice and offer optional excursions and walking passes.</em></p>
<p><em>Special diets, including vegetarian, must be requested prior to booking.</em></p>
<p><em>The itineraries may be subject to change. Where this becomes necessary, and where practicable, we will take the steps as outlined in clause 5 of our <a data-udi="umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">terms and conditions</a>.</em></p>]]></locationDescription>
